{"tid":1932874,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[FMDC-030]菲臘比美路：當年夾埋輪流侵犯美斯","createTime":"2020-03-19T03:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T05:49:34.000Z","uid":3747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2b983ab07ba90667d645aa2e8cf33ae1657b10","tid":1932874,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】老牌巴西防中菲臘比美路透露，當年對戰阿根廷時，一眾隊友輪流侵犯美斯，以打亂對方的比賽節奏。<br />\n<br />\n36歲的菲臘比美路（Felipe Melo）曾代表巴西國家隊上陣22次，踢過祖雲達斯、國際米蘭、加拉塔沙雷等歐洲名牌球隊，現時已回流巴甲，效力彭美拉斯。回想跟球王美斯（Lionel Messi）對撼，菲臘比美路說：「當巴西對他時，我們會輪流踢他一次，一個接一個，因為如果不是這樣，便難以阻止他。」他表示不是希望傷害美斯，純粹是戰術需要，「我們希望打斷他的節奏，擾亂他。」菲臘比美路以狠辣攔截聞名，他認為各地球證的風格不一：「在英國如果你踢中對手，球證不會判罰，但在西班牙你就會被罰出場，在巴西則五五波。若在南美自由盃，巴西球證會驅逐你，但阿根廷球證就不一定。」圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"b8977d3aefefbec70b12b9c7f286b3ccf58d0003","tid":1932874,"uid":214692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗性侵犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73f04e987c6fdb370e450066d8445bc0f000890","tid":1932874,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"在英國如果你踢中對手，球證不會判罰，但在西班牙你就會被罰出場，在巴西則五五波。若在南美自由盃，巴西球證會驅逐你，但阿根廷球證就不一定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece6fb4e5b9fde96af4095e4a3ba8a5054005e3d","tid":1932874,"uid":37948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:58:40.000Z","msg":"條茅柴對荷蘭場波仲好撚記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f63be25c93a729c7c3f9fb8719a4750c3b8e08b","tid":1932874,"uid":87471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:32:42.000Z","msg":"而家變左卡斯米路一人獨享侵犯美斯既權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63df5d7e17f0ad9d217d4ee51d9e413ec391e414","tid":1932874,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"輪姦小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d238e302a1db10cbf0e1f6ee164af66b81d77a","tid":1932874,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f63be25c93a729c7c3f9fb8719a4750c3b8e08b","tid":1932874,"uid":87471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:32:42.000Z","msg":"而家變左卡斯米路一人獨享侵犯美斯既權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"卡斯米路:在地球如果你踢中對手，球證不會判罰"},{"pid":"3c89848d8cd90404c12f78944499e6a8b72824cc","tid":1932874,"uid":347748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hx10zSO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhx10zSO.jpg&h=f72203fa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}